Maintainer: Joshua Marie <joshua.marie.k@gmail.com>
Description: Collection of functions to print the data frames in command line. 
    This package provides helpers to display a statistical results in a data frame,
    contingency table, correlation matrix, and a summary table in 2 columns form.
